    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">Dear colleague,</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">We are pleased to confirm the speaker line-up for our upcoming webinar, <strong>Empowering the Election Workforce: Global Survey Findings &amp; Solutions on Recruitment, Training, and Retention</strong>, taking place on <strong>Friday, 24 April at 14:00 BST (GMT+1)</strong>.</p>

    <p style="margin:0 0 18px; color:#333333; font-size:15px; line-height:1.6;">The session will present the results of a global workforce survey spanning 26 jurisdictions, followed by expert perspectives from academia, the field, and technology partners.</p>

